            <div class="bottom">
                <h3>Giraffes:</h3>
                <p>Say hello to our gentle giants, Skyler, the tallest in our park, and Luna, a young and curious
                    female.
                    These awe-inspiring creatures are known for their elongated necks and distinctive spotted patterns,
                    which provide camouflage in the wild. At our wildlife park, you can witness Skyler and Luna
                    gracefully
                    browsing on tree leaves and engaging in gentle interactions with each other. Learn about their
                    unique
                    physiology, social behaviors, and the ongoing conservation efforts to preserve their natural
                    habitats.
                </p>
